### BABY CLASS SKILLS CONTROLLER TESTING
### ===========================================

### 1. Get All Baby Class Skills
GET {{BluebirdCore_HostAddress}}/api/BabyClassSkills/skills
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get Skill Items for a Specific Skill
GET {{BluebirdCore_HostAddress}}/api/BabyClassSkills/skills/1/items
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Get Student Skill Assessments
GET {{BluebirdCore_HostAddress}}/api/BabyClassSkills/students/2007/assessments?academicYear=1&term=3
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Create or Update Skill Assessment
POST {{BluebirdCore_HostAddress}}/api/BabyClassSkills/assessments
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 2017,
  "skillItemId": 3,
  "academicYear": 1,
  "term": 3,
  "teacherComment": "Student shows good progress in this skill area."
}

###

### 5. Update Existing Assessment
PUT {{BluebirdCore_HostAddress}}/api/BabyClassSkills/assessments
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assessmentId": 1,
  "teacherComment": "Updated comment: Student has improved significantly."
}

###

### 6. Get Class Skill Assessments
GET {{BluebirdCore_HostAddress}}/api/BabyClassSkills/classes/1/assessments?academicYear=2024&term=1
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Delete Skill Assessment
